description: The City of Los Angeles Community Development Department, FamilySource Centers, provide a wealth of services and programs for families with children. Services are restricted to residents of the City of Los Angeles.   The system is comprised of a network of 21 community centers that deliver coordinated, outcome-driven services to city residents in areas of highest need.
